<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<feed xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><title>mqShen</title><link href="http://github.com/" rel="alternate"></link><link href="http://github.com/feeds/all.atom.xml" rel="self"></link><id>http://github.com/</id><updated>2013-01-14T00:00:00+08:00</updated><entry><title>pelican</title><link href="http://github.com/pelican.html" rel="alternate"></link><updated>2013-01-14T00:00:00+08:00</updated><author><name>mqShen</name></author><id>tag:github.com,2013-01-14:pelican.html</id><summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;今天把github上的Blog从octopress换成了&lt;a href="http://http://blog.getpelican.com/"&gt;pelican&lt;/a&gt;
以前那些文章写得太随意那我就把这篇作为第一篇吧。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1 id="0++++"&gt;0.环境介绍&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;OS: centos 6&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1 id="1++peclican"&gt;1.安装peclican&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;我是在github上下载了&lt;a href="https://github.com/getpelican/pelican.git"&gt;pelican&lt;/a&gt;的源码来安装的
    python setup.py install
我们还需要安装markdown依赖
    yum install python-markdown&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1 id="2settingspy"&gt;2.settings.py&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;div class="codehilite"&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class="c"&gt;# -*- coding: utf-8 -*-&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="n"&gt;import&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;sys&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class="n"&gt;TIMEZONE&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="p"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="s"&gt;&amp;#39;Asia/Shanghai&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class="n"&gt;DEFAULT_LANG&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="p"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="s"&gt;&amp;#39;zhs&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class="n"&gt;SITENAME&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="p"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="s"&gt;&amp;quot;mqShen&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="n"&gt;SITESUBTITLE&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="p"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="s"&gt;&amp;quot;simple simple simple&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="n"&gt;AUTHOR&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="p"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="s"&gt;&amp;#39;mqShen&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class="n"&gt;DISQUS_SITENAME&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="p"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="s"&gt;&amp;#39;mqShenblog&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="n"&gt;GITHUB_URL&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="p"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="s"&gt;&amp;#39;https://github.com/mqshen/mqshen.github.com&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="n"&gt;SITEURL&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="p"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="s"&gt;&amp;#39;http://mqshen.github.com&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="n"&gt;GOOGLE_ANALYTICS&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="p"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="s"&gt;&amp;#39;UA-30756331-1&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="c"&gt;#谷歌站点分析&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="n"&gt;TAG_FEED&lt;/span&gt;  &lt;span class="p"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="s"&gt;&amp;#39;feeds/%s.atom.xml&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class="n"&gt;DEFAULT_PAGINATION&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="p"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mi"&gt;4&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="c"&gt;#默认每一页有多少篇文章&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class="n"&gt;DEFAULT_CATEGORY&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="p"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s"&gt;&amp;#39;tech&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="n"&gt;OUTPUT_PATH&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="p"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="s"&gt;&amp;#39;output&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="c"&gt;#需要把输出路径从默认的&amp;#39;output&amp;#39;改成根目录(your_id.github.com目录), 因为githubpage需要把index.html上传到repo的master分支的根目录才可以!&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="n"&gt;PATH&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="p"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="s"&gt;&amp;#39;posts&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="c"&gt;#这个是指定放置.md/.rst文件的目录&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class="n"&gt;LINKS&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="p"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="p"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;
         &lt;span class="p"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="c"&gt;#友情链接~&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class="n"&gt;SOCIAL&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="p"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="p"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;
          &lt;span class="p"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s"&gt;&amp;#39;twitter&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="s"&gt;&amp;#39;http://twitter.com/mqshen&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;),&lt;/span&gt;
          &lt;span class="p"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s"&gt;&amp;#39;github&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="s"&gt;&amp;#39;https://github.com/mqshen&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;),&lt;/span&gt;
          &lt;span class="p"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="c"&gt;#社交网络链接&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;


&lt;h1 id="3+++"&gt;3.小脚本&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;为了方便使用我写了个小脚本
使用方法(需要在settings.py的目录下运行)
    myBlog newPost postTitle #创建新文章
    myBlog deploy commitMessage #提交到github上&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;脚本代码
    CURRENT_YEAR=&lt;code&gt;date +'%Y'&lt;/code&gt;
    CURRENT_MONTH=&lt;code&gt;date +'%m'&lt;/code&gt;
    CURRENT_DAY=&lt;code&gt;date +'%d'&lt;/code&gt;
    CURRENT_DATE=&lt;code&gt;date +'%Y-%m-%d'&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="codehilite"&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;POST_DIRECTORY&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="err"&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;posts&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="err"&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class="k"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="p"&gt;[&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="s"&gt;&amp;quot;$1&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;==&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="s"&gt;&amp;quot;newPost&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="p"&gt;];&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;then&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class="k"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;test&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;!&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;d&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="err"&gt;$&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;POST_DIRECTORY&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="err"&gt;$&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;CURRENT_YEAR&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="err"&gt;$&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;CURRENT_MONTH&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;then&lt;/span&gt;
        &lt;span class="n"&gt;echo&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="err"&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;create&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;directory&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="err"&gt;&amp;#39;$&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;POST_DIRECTORY&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="err"&gt;$&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;CURRENT_YEAR&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="err"&gt;$&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;CURRENT_MONTH&lt;/span&gt;
        &lt;span class="n"&gt;mkdir&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;p&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="err"&gt;$&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;POST_DIRECTORY&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="err"&gt;$&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;CURRENT_YEAR&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="err"&gt;$&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;CURRENT_MONTH&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class="n"&gt;fi&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class="k"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;test&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;f&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="err"&gt;$&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;POST_DIRECTORY&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="err"&gt;$&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;CURRENT_YEAR&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="err"&gt;$&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;CURRENT_MONTH&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="err"&gt;$&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="mf"&gt;2.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;md&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;then&lt;/span&gt;
        &lt;span class="n"&gt;echo&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="err"&gt;$&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;POST_DIRECTORY&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="err"&gt;$&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;CURRENT_YEAR&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="err"&gt;$&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;CURRENT_MONTH&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="err"&gt;$&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="mf"&gt;2.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;md&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="err"&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;is&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;exists&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="err"&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;
        &lt;span class="n"&gt;exit&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mi"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class="n"&gt;fi&lt;/span&gt; 
    &lt;span class="n"&gt;echo&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="err"&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;create&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;file&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="err"&gt;&amp;#39;$&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;POST_DIRECTORY&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="err"&gt;$&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;CURRENT_YEAR&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="err"&gt;$&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;CURRENT_MONTH&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="err"&gt;$&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="mf"&gt;2.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;md&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class="n"&gt;echo&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="err"&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;Date&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="err"&gt;&amp;#39;$&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;CURRENT_DATE&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;&amp;gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="err"&gt;$&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;POST_DIRECTORY&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="err"&gt;$&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;CURRENT_YEAR&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="err"&gt;$&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;CURRENT_MONTH&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="err"&gt;$&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="mf"&gt;2.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;md&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class="n"&gt;echo&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="err"&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;Title&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="err"&gt;&amp;#39;$&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="mi"&gt;2&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;&amp;gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="err"&gt;$&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;POST_DIRECTORY&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="err"&gt;$&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;CURRENT_YEAR&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="err"&gt;$&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;CURRENT_MONTH&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="err"&gt;$&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="mf"&gt;2.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;md&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class="n"&gt;echo&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="err"&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;Category&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="err"&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;&amp;gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="err"&gt;$&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;POST_DIRECTORY&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="err"&gt;$&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;CURRENT_YEAR&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="err"&gt;$&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;CURRENT_MONTH&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="err"&gt;$&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="mf"&gt;2.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;md&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class="n"&gt;echo&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="err"&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;Tags&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="err"&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;&amp;gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="err"&gt;$&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;POST_DIRECTORY&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="err"&gt;$&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;CURRENT_YEAR&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="err"&gt;$&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;CURRENT_MONTH&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="err"&gt;$&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="mf"&gt;2.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;md&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class="n"&gt;exit&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mi"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="n"&gt;fi&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class="k"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="p"&gt;[&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="s"&gt;&amp;quot;$1&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;==&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="s"&gt;&amp;quot;deploy&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="p"&gt;];&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;then&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class="n"&gt;pelican&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="p"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;t&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="p"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;s&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;settings&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;py&lt;/span&gt; 
    &lt;span class="n"&gt;cd&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;output&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class="n"&gt;git&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;add&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="p"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class="n"&gt;git&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;commit&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;m&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="err"&gt;$&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="mi"&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class="n"&gt;git&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;push&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class="n"&gt;exit&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mi"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="n"&gt;fi&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</summary><category term="peclican"></category></entry></feed>